// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0547 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c8d3ea17-3a52-5732-996d-65ada241f06a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:17.04*")
